@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nuvpeu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.sin((v1 + 0.64 * v0 + 0.81)))
    v1 = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.83 + v1 + 0.83) * (tmp + 0.60 + v2 + 0.48)))
    v2 = wp.sin((0.14 / wp.sin(tmp + 0.08)))
    v2 = ((0.92 + 0.24) / ((v1 + 0.68 / v1 + 0.40) + (v0 + 0.09 * v2 + 0.83)))
    v2 = wp.cos((v0 * (v0 + 0.00 * tmp + 0.32)))
    v1 = v2
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
